      "role": "user",
      "content": "but you don't get it. it's not just a \"rough patch\" or being sad. it's like the actual substance of me is gone. if the art was the thing that gave me meaning, and that's dead... then what's even the point of the rest of it? i feel like i'm just performing being a person, but there's no one actually home anymore. it feels so heavy to just keep dragging this empty vessel around.",
